<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Recipes4U</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <h1>Recipes4U</h1>
    <a href="login">
        <div id="userProfileIcon">
            <img src="images/user.png">
            <p>Login</p>
            <div id="userProfileDropdown">
                <ul>
                    <li>My Account</li>
                    <li>Settings</li>
                    <li>Log Out</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>
</header>
<main>
    <div id="searchBar">
        <b>What would you like to cook today?</b>
        <p>Anything you would like to cook, you can input here.</p>
        <div class="search-bar">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Search recipes..." id="search-input">
            <button type="submit" id="search-button">Search</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="ingredientOwn">
        <b>Fill in the box below with ingredients that you own!</b>
        <p>We can find you available recipes based on your input.</p>
        <div id="ingredientInputWrapper">
            <textarea id="ingredients-input" name="enter your ingredients here..." cols="50" rows="10"></textarea>
            <button id="enter-button">Enter</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="restaurant-advisor">
        <h2>üçΩÔ∏è Need a place to eat?</h2>
        <p>If you're not in the mood to cook, let us suggest a restaurant based on your ingredients!</p>
    
        <form class="search-form" action="/recommendation/advisersubmit" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="recipeText" placeholder="Enter a ingredient..." required>
            <button class="btn" type="submit">Find Restaurants</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        #restaurant-advisor {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 50vh; /* Centers vertically */
        }
    
        .search-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }
    
        .search-form input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    
        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
    
    <div id="ingredientList">
        <b>You can also press and hold on any of the common ingredients from below.</b>
    </div>

    <div id="ingredientNumTest">
        <label for="recipe-count"> Number of recipes</label>
        <input type="number" id="recipeCount" min="1" max="10" value="1">
    </div>

    <div id="recipeOutput">
        <h2>Generated Recipe:</h2>
        <div id="recipe-text"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="authLinks">
        <a href="savedRecipes">Saved Recipes</a>
    </div>
</main>
<script type= "module" src="js/gpt_handler.js"></script>
<script src="js/mainPage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
